.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-ACCESS-SERVICE-ACCOUNT-TOKEN 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-access\-service\-account\-token \- Add or delete tokens for a Grafana service account.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util access service-account token [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Add or delete tokens for a Grafana service account.
.IP \(bu 2
Create a new service\-account token.
.IP \(bu 2
Delete an existing service\-account token by service\-account name or id.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B add
\-\-service\-account\-id or \-\-name, \-\-token\-name, \-\-seconds\-to\-live, \-\-json
.TP
.B delete
\-\-service\-account\-id or \-\-name, \-\-token\-name, \-\-yes, \-\-json
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Add or delete tokens for a Grafana service account.
.EX
grafana-util access service-account token add --profile prod --name deploy-bot --token-name nightly
.EE
.PP
Add or delete tokens for a Grafana service account.
.EX
grafana-util access service-account token delete --profile prod --name deploy-bot --token-name nightly --yes --json
.EE
